Package com.nmoumoulidis.opensensor.view

Class Summary
AdminActivity UI class for the Administrator Settings feature.
GeneralSpinnerAdapter UI utility class for populating the spinners (drop-down menus) that live in the SensorStationActivity and ServerActivity.
MainActivity The main UI class, launched when the user launches the app.
PhoneSensActivity UI skeleton class of the non-implemented phone-sensor feature.
SensorStationActivity UI class for the Wi-Fi connecter OpenSensor Station features: real-time data requests and browse recently received batch data from it.
SensorStationDataListViewAdapter UI utility class, used to populate data results in a structured way using the powerful SimpleCursorAdapter Android class.
SensorStationDatePickerFragment Date-picker UI element for the OpenSensor Station search query features.
ServerActivity UI class for the server-based data browsing feature (OpenSensor Server).
ServerDataListViewAdapter UI utility class, used to populate data results in a structured way using the powerful SimpleCursorAdapter Android class.
ServerDatePickerFragment Date-picker UI element for the OpenSensor Server search query features.
